# (as in lj/class2/soft, already ported in pair_lj_class2_soft_omp.cpp) with
# Ewald-softcore Coulomb (as in lj/cut/coul/long/soft, already ported in
# pair_lj_cut_coul_long_soft_omp.cpp). lambda=0.7 keeps both softcore alpha terms
# (lj3, lj4) non-zero so the full eval() arithmetic (denc, denlj, pow(denlj,-2.5))
